perl-net-http (Low-level HTTP connection client)

The Net::HTTP class is a low-level HTTP client. An instance of the
Net::HTTP class represents a connection to an HTTP server.
The HTTP protocol is described in RFC 2616. The Net::HTTP class
supports HTTP/1.0 and HTTP/1.1.

HOME: https://github.com/libwww-perl/Net-HTTP

